Class ExceptionalWrapper

java.lang.Object
net.dapete.exceptional.ExceptionalWrapper
public final class ExceptionalWrapper extends Object
Utility class to wrap exceptions thrown in lambas from the net.dapete.exceptional.function package in runtime exceptions of type WrappedExceptionalException, or leave them as they are if they are already runtime exceptions.
